divs: sighting detailsdear oc mufon, i am a member of your organization and have tried to email you at info@ocmufon.org about this but received a message from the "postmaster" that this is not a valid email address. so i apologize for inquiring in this form but really would like some answers. this sighting was not my own, but i discovered it on abovetopsecret.com today. supposedly there was a major ufo event over the skies of oc in the early evening of 01\26\08 that was witnessed by many. there has been no media coverage and the topic is currently being discussed on abovetopsecret.com. the original source is www.americanchronicle.com. is this a big hoax? i am especially interested because it is almost exactly like a sighting i had on 3\26\06 right here in my own backyard in irvine. any info you can provide would be most helpful. thanks, mary
Summary: Two fireballs, maybe a small blue light also
